---
import ContentWidth from "./ContentWidth.astro";
---

<section id="noticias" class="relative py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <ContentWidth>
        <div class="relative z-10 mb-16 md:flex items-end justify-between gap-6">
            <div class="max-w-2xl">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-[#d4a017]"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#002850]">
                        Prensa y Actualidad
                    </span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-[#003d82] leading-tight">
                    Martín Salas en <span class="text-[#d4a017]">los Medios</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0">
                <a href="/noticias" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#003d82] font-bold hover:text-[#d4a017] transition-colors group">
                    VER TODAS LAS NOTICIAS
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative z-10">

            <article class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                    <img
                            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829545856-d10d557cf95f?q=80&w=800"
                            alt="Entrevista en TV"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                        <span class="bg-[#003d82] text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Entrevista</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                    <time class="text-xs font-bold text-[#d4a017] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">15 de Marzo, 2024</time>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#002850] mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#003d82] transition-colors">
                        "La reforma del sistema de justicia no puede esperar más"
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 line-clamp-3">
                        En una entrevista exclusiva para un medio nacional, Martín Salas detalló los pilares de su propuesta legislativa para fortalecer la fiscalía...
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-50">
                        <span class="text-[#003d82] font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                            LEER MÁS
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                    <img
                            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529107386315-e1a2ed48a620?q=80&w=800"
                            alt="Reunión con gremios"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                        <span class="bg-[#003d82] text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Campaña</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                    <time class="text-xs font-bold text-[#d4a017] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">12 de Marzo, 2024</time>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#002850] mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#003d82] transition-colors">
                        Encuentro con líderes vecinales en Lima Norte
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 line-clamp-3">
                        Continuando con las jornadas de escucha activa, Salas se reunió con representantes de organizaciones sociales para discutir seguridad...
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-50">
                        <span class="text-[#003d82] font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                            LEER MÁS
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                    <img
                            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?q=80&w=800"
                            alt="Propuestas de ley"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                        <span class="bg-[#d4a017] text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Propuesta</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                    <time class="text-xs font-bold text-[#d4a017] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">08 de Marzo, 2024</time>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#002850] mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#003d82] transition-colors">
                        Plan "Tolerancia Cero": Estrategia frontal contra el soborno
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 line-clamp-3">
                        Presentación del paquete legislativo que busca inhabilitar de por vida a funcionarios públicos sentenciados por delitos de corrupción...
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-50">
                        <span class="text-[#003d82] font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                            LEER MÁS
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

        </div>
    </ContentWidth>
</section>